channel.title: Starting server on moparisthebest.com
channel.description:
Guys, can someone tell me how to start server on moparisthebest.com
When I get loaded client, I click start server and than I log in. After that it says error connection to server,.... And after that it says:
Server: Error: Unable to startup listener on 43594 - port already in use?
Can someone please help me?

item.title: Starting server on moparisthebest.com
item.dc:creator: @Skyro Arbe
item.description:
@Skyro wrote:

Port 43594 is already in-use, try and see what’s using that port so you can stop it and run your server.

Read full topic
